<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to My E-Commerce Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #001a33; /* Dark blue background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h2, h3, p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        p {
            color: #cfd8dc; /* Light grey for better readability */
            text-align: center;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        ul li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0a2540, #001a33); /* Gradient background */
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .categories {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .category-card {
            background-color: #0a2540;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .category-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .category-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .call-to-action {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .call-to-action a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f97316, #ec4899);
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .call-to-action a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ec4899, #f97316); /* Reverse gradient */
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .categories {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            .category-card {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('header') %>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to My E-Commerce Store</h1>
            <p>Your trusted destination for quality products, amazing deals, and a seamless shopping experience.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>
                At <strong>My E-Commerce Store</strong>, we pride ourselves on being the go-to platform for online shopping. Here's why customers love us:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Wide Variety:</strong> Electronics, fashion, home essentials, and more.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Trust:</strong> Thousands of satisfied shoppers and stellar reviews.</li>
                <li><strong>Fast Delivery:</strong> Quick shipping and secure payments guaranteed.</li>
                <li><strong>Exclusive Deals:</strong> Daily discounts you wonâ€™t find anywhere else.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="products">
            <h2>Shop by Category</h2>
            <p>Explore our wide range of products:</p>
            <div class="categories">
                <div class="category-card">
                    <h3>Electronics</h3>
                    <p>Top-quality gadgets and accessories at unbeatable prices.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="category-card">
                    <h3>Fashion</h3>
                    <p>Stay stylish with our curated collection of apparel and accessories.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="category-card">
                    <h3>Home Essentials</h3>
                    <p>Everything you need to make your house a home.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="category-card">
                    <h3>Gifts & More</h3>
                    <p>Find the perfect present for any occasion.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <h2>Ready to Shop?</h2>
            <p>Join thousands of happy customers and start your shopping journey today.</p>
            <a href="/products">Shop Now</a>
        </section>
    </div>
    <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>